in low-light environments, aging impact on facial features, and handling occlusions. These challenges push the boundaries of AI technology and foster innovation in image processing, neural network architectures, and data security.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In conclusion, AI-based facial recognition systems are highly relevant in both practical and academic contexts. Their development contributes significantly to security improvements, while academic research continues to drive advancements in this rapidly evolving field.<\\/p>\",\"seo_title\":\"AI-Based Facial Recognition System: Technology, Importance, and Applications in Academic Research\",\"seo_description\":\"Explore AI facial recognition technology, its applications, and significance in academic research\",\"seo_keyword\":\"AI facial recognition, facial recognition technology, AI security, CNN, OpenCV, TensorFlow, Dlib, research\",\"_token\":\"o4YssJqpZthiGilljcK0nCmNgjJXYzpCvUewTKrM\",\"_method\":\"PUT\"}', '2024-09-24 18:12:54', '2024-09-24 18:12:54'),
